**Glary Utilities** is a comprehensive system optimization and maintenance tool designed to improve performance, stability, and security of Windows-based systems.

This repository provides an overview of the application, its core functionality, and general use cases.

---

## 🚀 Overview

Glary Utilities combines multiple system tools into a single interface, allowing users to clean, optimize, manage, and protect their computers efficiently.

It is suitable for both regular users and advanced users who need deeper control over system maintenance.

---

## ✨ Features

- System cleanup and junk file removal  
- Registry cleaning and repair  
- Startup and service management  
- Memory and performance optimization  
- Disk and file management tools  
- Privacy and security utilities  
- Simple and advanced modes for different user levels  

---

## 🖥️ Use Cases

- Improving overall system performance  
- Cleaning unnecessary files and registry entries  
- Managing startup programs  
- Freeing disk space  
- Maintaining system stability over time  

